    <item>
      <title>Best Navigation Systems for Camper Vans (What We Used &#43; What&#39;s Better Now)</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/gear/kenwood-dnx574s-navigation-head-unit-review/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/gear/kenwood-dnx574s-navigation-head-unit-review/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Best Navigation Systems for Camper Vans (What We Used + What&amp;rsquo;s Better Now)&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;best-navigation-systems-for-camper-vans-what-we-used--whats-better-now&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#best-navigation-systems-for-camper-vans-what-we-used--whats-better-now&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I spent seven years full-time in a 2017 Dodge ProMaster 2500, and one underrated upgrade was replacing the factory head unit with a more capable navigation and media system. Good route planning, better audio integration, and smoother device connectivity improve daily drive quality and reduce friction on long travel days. This review covers the Kenwood DNX574S from that real-use perspective.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Bluetti Elite 200 V2 Power Station Review for Van Life</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/gear/bluetti-elite-200-v2-power-station-review/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/gear/bluetti-elite-200-v2-power-station-review/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Bluetti Elite 200 V2 Power Station Review for Van Life&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;bluetti-elite-200-v2-power-station-review-for-van-life&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#bluetti-elite-200-v2-power-station-review-for-van-life&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I lived full-time in a 2017 Dodge ProMaster 2500 for seven years, and I learned quickly that your power setup can make or break your day. If your battery system is unstable, everything gets harder: work, cooking, sleep, and basic comfort. I tested the Bluetti Elite 200 V2 as a practical, all-in-one option for van lifers who want less wiring complexity and more reliable daily power. This review is based on how it performs in real van conditions, not lab-only numbers.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Remote Work Gear for Vans</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/gear/remote-work-gear-for-vans/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/gear/remote-work-gear-for-vans/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;You do not need a luxury build to work online from your van. Focus on power stability, internet uptime, and ergonomic basics.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Best Budget Remote Work Picks&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;best-budget-remote-work-picks&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#best-budget-remote-work-picks&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Portable 15.6&amp;quot; USB-C Monitor&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;portable-156-usb-c-monitor&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#portable-156-usb-c-monitor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Pros: dual-screen productivity at low cost.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Cons: fragile panels need padded storage.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;CTA: &lt;a href=&#34;&#34; &gt;See Portable Monitor Deals&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Logitech MX Anywhere 3S&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;logitech-mx-anywhere-3s&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#logitech-mx-anywhere-3s&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Pros: compact, reliable on many surfaces.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Cons: premium price versus entry mice.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;CTA: &lt;a href=&#34;&#34; &gt;Shop Logitech MX Anywhere&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Anker 7-in-1 USB-C Hub&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;anker-7-in-1-usb-c-hub&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#anker-7-in-1-usb-c-hub&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Pros: adds ports fast for laptops/tablets.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Cons: heat build-up under heavy use.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;CTA: &lt;a href=&#34;&#34; &gt;Check Hub Pricing&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Noise-Isolating USB Headset&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;noise-isolating-usb-headset&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#noise-isolating-usb-headset&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Pros: cleaner call audio in noisy camp spots.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Cons: wired models can clutter a small desk.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;CTA: &lt;a href=&#34;&#34; &gt;View Budget Headsets&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Internet and Wi-Fi Boosters for Van Life</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/gear/internet-wifi-boosters-for-van-life/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/gear/internet-wifi-boosters-for-van-life/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Reliable internet is critical if you work remotely or stream on the road. These options balance cost and reliability.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Recommended Connectivity Gear&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;recommended-connectivity-gear&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#recommended-connectivity-gear&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;weBoost Drive Reach&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;weboost-drive-reach&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#weboost-drive-reach&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Pros: stronger fringe-area signal, durable hardware.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Cons: higher upfront cost than passive options.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;CTA: &lt;a href=&#34;&#34; &gt;Check weBoost Pricing&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;GL.iNet Spitz AX Router&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;glinet-spitz-ax-router&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#glinet-spitz-ax-router&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Pros: multi-carrier flexibility, advanced controls.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Cons: steeper setup for non-technical users.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;CTA: &lt;a href=&#34;&#34; &gt;View GL.iNet Router&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;NETGEAR Nighthawk M6 (used/refurb deals)&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;netgear-nighthawk-m6-usedrefurb-deals&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#netgear-nighthawk-m6-usedrefurb-deals&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Pros: excellent speeds where coverage is strong.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Cons: can exceed budget new.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;CTA: &lt;a href=&#34;&#34; &gt;Find Nighthawk Deals&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Poynting Omni Antenna&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;poynting-omni-antenna&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#poynting-omni-antenna&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Pros: better rooftop reception for LTE/5G routers.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Cons: requires proper mounting and cable routing.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;CTA: &lt;a href=&#34;&#34; &gt;Shop Poynting Antenna&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Portable Power Stations Under $500</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/gear/portable-power-stations-under-500/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/gear/portable-power-stations-under-500/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;If you want plug-and-play power without a full electrical build, these units offer the best value for everyday van life.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Top Budget Power Stations&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;top-budget-power-stations&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#top-budget-power-stations&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;EcoFlow RIVER 2 Pro&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;ecoflow-river-2-pro&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#ecoflow-river-2-pro&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Pros: fast recharge, lightweight, reliable app.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Cons: premium pricing during non-sale periods.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;CTA: &lt;a href=&#34;&#34; &gt;Check EcoFlow Price&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;BLUETTI EB55&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;bluetti-eb55&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#bluetti-eb55&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Pros: good port variety, solid battery life.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Cons: heavier than similar-capacity models.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;CTA: &lt;a href=&#34;&#34; &gt;View BLUETTI Deals&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Jackery Explorer 300 Plus&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;jackery-explorer-300-plus&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#jackery-explorer-300-plus&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Pros: compact and beginner-friendly.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Cons: lower output for power-hungry appliances.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;CTA: &lt;a href=&#34;&#34; &gt;Shop Jackery 300 Plus&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Anker SOLIX C800 (sale-dependent under $500)&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;anker-solix-c800-sale-dependent-under-500&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#anker-solix-c800-sale-dependent-under-500&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Pros: high output for cost, good brand support.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Cons: often near the top of the budget cap.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;CTA: &lt;a href=&#34;&#34; &gt;See Latest Anker Offer&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
      
